<div id="review_1680435582" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1680435582" />
    <a title="Mohammed Morsi" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/56936977-mohammed-morsi"><img alt="Mohammed Morsi" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1466318668p2/56936977.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1680435582?book_show_action=true">Jan 21, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Mohammed Morsi" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Mohammed Morsi" href="/user/show/56936977-mohammed-morsi">Mohammed Morsi</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1680435582" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2424574730586762772">A must read for those who do not know of Ibn Battuta. Well written and documented, it carries you through the journeys and offers a different view than the contemporary, and better known but perhaps less travelled, Marco Polo.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


