<div id="review_3828438134" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3828438134" />
    <a title="Christopher" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/10853489-christopher"><img alt="Christopher" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1385004844p2/10853489.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3828438134?book_show_action=true">Feb 09, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Christopher" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Christopher" href="/user/show/10853489-christopher">Christopher</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover " href="/book/show/16110747-the-travels-of-ibn-battutah">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3828438134" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16934439770522061040">From 1325 to 1356, Ibn Battutah, an Islamic scholar and lawyer, traveled through North Africa, the Middle East, Arabia, India, China, and West Africa, at times spending years in one place serving as a qadi or judge of Islamic law. His description of his travels, the places he visited, and cultures he encountered is a fascinating read. It’s a good counterpoint to the travels of Marco Polo, who covered much of the same ground a generation earlier.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

