        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3992555318" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2976821748025875880">I&apos;ll have to admit defeat. Battutah&apos;s travelogue is both the details of getting-there and anecdotes about the places he visits. While the latter is frequently interesting, the former smacks of sitting through a relative&apos;s over-detailed travel photo album, where every meal is documented and every taxi is photographed. There&apos;s no joy in reading the minutia and I haven&apos;t the patience to skip through and figure out if the style changes later.</span>
  <span id="freeText2976821748025875880" style="display:none">I'll have to admit defeat. Battutah's travelogue is both the details of getting-there and anecdotes about the places he visits. While the latter is frequently interesting, the former smacks of sitting through a relative's over-detailed travel photo album, where every meal is documented and every taxi is photographed. There's no joy in reading the minutia and I haven't the patience to skip through and figure out if the style changes later.</span>
